Annotations.Annotation: Michigan Behavioral Risk Factor Surveillance System
Michigan Behavioral Risk Factor Surveillance System

The Michigan Behavioral Risk Factor Surveillance System (MiBRFSS) is composed of annual, state-level telephone surveys of Michigan residents, aged 18 years and older. Some data is only available for a limited portion of Wayne County.
